00:06:05.320 --> 00:06:07.010
GERARDO ADESSO: And then there
is another, for instance

00:06:07.010 --> 00:06:09.590
another one which
42 belongs to.

00:06:09.590 --> 00:06:13.150
It's the sequence of
harshad numbers.

00:06:13.150 --> 00:06:14.890
Harshad is written like this.

00:06:14.890 --> 00:06:16.990
So what is a harshad number?

00:06:16.990 --> 00:06:20.620
It's a number that
is divisible by

00:06:20.620 --> 00:06:23.110
